{"tid":510681,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【氣象】（2017年12月下旬末）偏東氣流影響廣東沿岸，本港雲量稍為增多","createTime":"2017-12-26T16:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T05:42:52.000Z","uid":44630,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"50befd182c9baacd3af19800467d146d99ac8690","tid":510681,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T16:54:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\"><img src=\"http://imgur.com/fxgjJzQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FfxgjJzQ.png&h=e15d1b57&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>氣象討論：2017年12月下旬末</ins></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">此帖文討論期：2017年12月27日至31日</span></span></strong><br />\n【註】 氣象討論帖一般逢每月1日、11日及21日發出新帖文。　當新帖文發出後，或有颱風追擊帖發出，原有的氣象討論帖會隨即停用。　為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">氣象台專頁現已登場</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://x.co/FBlike\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FFBlike&h=5fdd3157&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://fb.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2FHKGweather&d=pXA423WqTMHD%2FZ%2Bkl25SD%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=7ef620f1\" target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/HKGweather</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://x.co/TWlike\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FTWlike&h=e9b064ef&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://twitter.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKGweather&d=pXA423WqTMHD%2FZ%2Bkl25SD%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=6ac4da68\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/HKGweather</a></span></em><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/BZfpfrS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBZfpfrS.png&h=9df3da65&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://youtube.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=h